6.10	Mark_Horton_(archaeologist)	Mark Horton (archaeologist)	He is the youngest of four children, the oldest being the industrialist Sir Robert Horton. He is married to archaeologist Catherine (Kate) Clark, Director of the Historic Houses Trust of New South Wales, and they have three children, Jack, Henrietta and Owen.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/53/Mark_Horton_Chepstow.jpg/220px-Mark_Horton_Chepstow.jpg
